Package structs

Class NodeStruct

  • java.lang.Object
    • structs.NodeStruct
  • public class NodeStruct
extends java.lang.Object
    The NodeStruct class represents a node in a network with its properties.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field Description
      double dailydemand
      The daily demand of the node in liters per day.
      double demand
      The demand of the node in liters per second.
      double elevation
      The elevation of the node in meters.
      int esr
      The ID of the ESR (Emergency Service Responder) node serving this node.
      double head
      The water head of the node in meters.
      double minpressure
      The minimum pressure required at the node in meters.
      int nodeid
      The unique integer ID of the node.
      java.lang.String nodename
      The name of the node.
      double pressure
      The water pressure of the node in meters (pressure = head - elevation).
